Let's consider:

greux:~> sleep 2&
[1] 20823
greux:~>
[1]  + done       sleep 2
greux:~>

The "[1] 20823" line is sent to stderr, whereas the "[1]  + done ..."
line is sent to stdout (I could see that with the coloring of stderr).
Is there any reason?

